---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<BaseLayout title="Ethics" description="Ethical clearance — risk, participant protection, and data handling">
  <p class="back-link"><a href={`${base}methods/`}>← Methods</a></p>
  <h1>Ethics</h1>

  <section class="methods-section">
    <p>
      <strong>Ethical clearance is very important.</strong> Do not collect primary data before you have clearance.
    </p>
    <p>There is a lot to consider in the ethical clearance process.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>For the university: what is the <strong>level of risk</strong> associated with the study?</li>
      <li>Am I bringing those people to some level of risk?</li>
      <li>How will you <strong>protect the data</strong>?</li>
      <li>How will you ensure <strong>anonymity</strong>?</li>
      <li>What measures will you take?</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .back-link {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  .back-link a {
    color: var(--color-maroon);
  }
  .methods-section {
    max-width: 720px;
  }
  .methods-section p {
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }
  .methods-section ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }
  .methods-section li {
    margin-bottom: 0.65rem;
  }
  .methods-section li:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
</style>
